These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Pet: fish, chinchilla, snake, frog
Cigar: ritmeester, bolivar, bongani, prince
1. Pet:snake is between Cigar:bongani and Cigar:bolivar##2
2. Pet:frog is on the left or right of Cigar:bongani##3
3. Cigar:bongani is not to the left of Cigar:bongani##8
4. Cigar:bolivar != Pet:snake##6
5. Pet:snake is somewhere to the right of Pet:fish##5
6. Pet:fish is on the right of Cigar:ritmeester##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Pet   | frog  | fish | snake | chinchilla  |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | bongani   | prince  | bolivar |

