.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Nationality: colombian, egyptian, german, argentine
Pet: horse, hedgehog, fish, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is not to the left of Pet:mouse##8
2. Nationality:colombian is somewhere to the right of Nationality:argentine##5
3. Nationality:colombian == Pet:hedgehog##1
4. Nationality:argentine is between Nationality:colombian and Nationality:egyptian##2
5. Nationality:egyptian is somewhere between Nationality:german and Pet:horse##7
6. Pet:fish is somewhere to the left of Nationality:egyptian##5
7. Pet:horse is not to the left of Pet:horse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | german | egyptian          | argentine | colombian     |
| Pet    | fish      | mouse | horse | hedgehog |

