.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Color: emerald, red, mauve, amber
Music-Genre: soul, r&b, country, metal
1. Music-Genre:soul is not to the left of Color:mauve##8
2. Music-Genre:r&b is on the far left##1
3. Color:red is on the right of Color:emerald##1
4. Color:red is in an even position##4
5. Color:amber is on the far left or far right##3
6. Color:emerald is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:metal##5
7. Color:amber == Music-Genre:country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color           | emerald | red | mauve     | amber |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | metal   | soul | country    |

