5. Pet:turtle == Food:peas##1
6. Pet:turtle is on the right of Food:corn##1
7. Pet:lizard is somewhere to the left of Pet:guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Pet   | lizard   | rat         | guinea-pig   | turtle    |
