 6. Pet:guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
 7. Pet:guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
 8. Sport:surfing is not to the right of Pet:goldfish##8
 9. Pet:guinea-pig is not to the left of Sport:surfing##8
